    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "起点是Broker，然后进入idle状态等待。当收到DECODE指令时，从idle跳转到parsing状态开始解析数据包。这个DECODE事件要标注来自MQTT Broker。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "idle",
        "parsing",
        "DECODE",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出Broker到idle，以及idle到parsing的DECODE转换。接下来parsing之后是什么状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
